text:
@hanichann    back when T-ARA was one of the top tier groups ( tied to Girls generation and 2ne1) haters basically claimed that T-ARA's members bullied hwayoung (she was a new member back then)
It was started when T-ARA had their first independent show in japan. Hwayoung claimed to suffer a serious leg injury 2 days prior to their show. When they arrived in Japan, hwayoung was walking normally until people started to take photos of her. Doctor stated that her leg was fine but she insisted on getting a cast and wheelchair.
On the first day of the show hwayoung only performed one song while sitting down. After the show ended, the original members tweeted about determination. This is when people speculated that they bullied hwayoung. Hwayoung and her twin sister milking this by playing victim. The allegation got so out of control with haters and hwayoung stans pulled out false evidences based on incomplete variety show clips and small accidents (e.g when hyomin accidentally poked hwayoung's face)

The only way to clear out the scandal was that hwayoung explained to the public.
However, she kept playing victim and people fell for it. T-ARA was being dragged for bullying
